### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000

### Sign Up
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Sign In
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get User Profile (requires JWT token)
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get User Profile via User Controller
GET http://localhost:3000/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Update User Profile
PATCH http://localhost:3000/user/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Updated Name"
}

### Get User Stats
GET http://localhost:3000/user/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Change Password
PATCH http://localhost:3000/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "currentPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### Forgot Password
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### Get All Skilltrees
GET http://localhost:3000/skilltree
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Skilltree
POST http://localhost:3000/skilltree
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Sample Skilltree",
  "description": "A sample skilltree for testing"
}

### Get User Skilltrees
GET http://localhost:3000/skilltree/user
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Specific Skilltree
GET http://localhost:3000/skilltree/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Update Skilltree
PATCH http://localhost:3000/skilltree/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Updated Skilltree Title"
}

### Delete Skilltree
DELETE http://localhost:3000/skilltree/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
